entries.entry: We installed everything needed for the program journey and learned some basics of our terminal.
We talked about HTML components and how to make grid layouts with Flexbox in CSS.
We learned how to navigate github and set up our first repository.
We did our first group project using HTML & CSS, then demoed it for the class.
We did our second group project using JavaScript and also demoed it for the class.
We took a look into json & postman and started to learn the basics about those things.
